items.title: Trump delays 50% tariffs on EU to July 9
items.description: President of the European Commission Ursula Von der Leyen said that she had a "good call" with Trump, but needed until July 9 to "reach a good deal."

items.title: House Speaker Johnson downplays deficit concerns as budget bill faces skeptics in Senate
